#Command line to compile this example:

g++ LoadShaders.cpp  example1-1.cpp -lglfw3 -framework Cocoa -framework OpenGL -framework IOKit -framework CoreVideo -lGLEW -o example1-1

The files here are listed on the book as:

main.cpp		example1.1
triangles.vert		example1.2
triangles.frag		example1.3

The other files are either on the “lib” or “include” folders in the original book code folder (link on the project README file).
